{"tid":1468964,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[機場事後檢討] 真 P 有野想講","createTime":"2019-08-13T23:43:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T23:47:02.000Z","uid":283657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"db7b0d47c7aba9309bef77a6495a15f3c8d82031","tid":1468964,"uid":283657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T23:43:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我唔係要分化割蓆 不過我哋真係要檢討下幾樣野！</strong></span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />昨日佔領機場及粗暴阻止旅客登機真係錯曬，這種以達到自己的目的為借口完全不理別人的需要與林鄭有何分別？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港可以把事件帶到外國層面，但絕對不是以這種以暴力縛架外國人而達成，這樣又與極權政府所做有何不同？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我絕不同意這種視香港問題比外國人的其他問題都重要的幼稚及不成熟亦不公平的睇法，我不相信＂勇武派＂這種自私唯我的心態會得到任何國家的真心支持，讓我感覺他們因生氣已失去應有的理智，而既然沒有了應有的理智，其他香港人又怎能依靠他們呢。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港問題，香港人自己解決，絕對不應將無辜的外國人牽涉在內，這實在令人反感。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"> <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>REPEAT: <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我唔係要分化割蓆 不過我哋真係要檢討下幾樣野！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n1. 唔好比狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />動搖到，佢要扮鬼發癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，係佢立場係合法嘅，因為警察實唔會交人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，而會有真人蒙上罪名。狗依架做野係冇準則架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，再係咁只會無限送頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，無補於事。<br />\n<br />\n2. 目標要清晰，冷靜處理同分析所有野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，一兩個消息已經可以令局勢緊張<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，所以唔好人云亦云。記得要冷靜諗一諗，三思而後行。<br />\n<br />\n3. 機場同係街唔同，有好多遊客，要令外國人支持我哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，因為好多外國人唔知香港發生咩事 ，搞到佢只會矛頭直指我哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。之後整幾多文宣都冇用。<br />\n<br />\n4. 本人一直都覺得和理非<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其實係口裏說不，身體卻很誠實，大難臨頭各自飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，所以前線唔好侍住有和理非，做一啲令和理非好難接受嘅事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，和理非好緊要，有文宣，有人數，有說服力，所以唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />失去佢哋。<br />\n<br />\n5. 前線真係要有幾個基本嘅規則e.g. 唔可阻醫護做嘢，唔可以推撞記者，etc. 呢個亦可幫捉鬼，因為佢哋會想做成傷亡<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">PS: 今次一定要贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n從來歷史書都係勝利嘅人寫嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n贏嘅就叫革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 輸嘅就叫叛亂<br />\n我們要名留青史定遺臭萬年就真係睇今舖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望各位手足唔好放棄，要力爭到底<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有朝一日，大家可以除低gear，為勝利乾杯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n#天佑香港</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"946fd9c0b3b77b837e7256ca0e1a8eb771b9c3d8","tid":1468964,"uid":283657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T23:44:00.000Z","msg":"PUSH x 1"},{"pid":"b1e247f800320db577d13c9944bba57f11bcf388","tid":1468964,"uid":283657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T23:44:14.000Z","msg":"PUSH x 2"},{"pid":"60ee63acd3889519ea13a2aa9dc51ceb2462ac94","tid":1468964,"uid":283657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T23:44:24.000Z","msg":"PUSH x 3"},{"pid":"aff2f196927466cecdb1a6d61793dbddd8b15340","tid":1468964,"uid":283657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T23:44:34.000Z","msg":"PUSH x 4"},{"pid":"179b5a219d02bb9b861d9330cd4cffe8fff56d84","tid":1468964,"uid":283657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T23:44:45.000Z","msg":"PUSH x 5"},{"pid":"583541f2f2f8d30f2a498197ac6650557481eab9","tid":1468964,"uid":283657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T23:44:59.000Z","msg":"PUSH x 6"},{"pid":"895dd3afaf5d6642be79be2ff6be0a13f54ecf85","tid":1468964,"uid":283657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T23:45:09.000Z","msg":"PUSH x 7"},{"pid":"0153a7f3ccc701fb84c7b623e31991169b3eb98e","tid":1468964,"uid":283657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T23:45:22.000Z","msg":"PUSH x 8"},{"pid":"275f2026f5f2cfec0eccd6d4822f52f852bfcac8","tid":1468964,"uid":283657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T23:45:32.000Z","msg":"PUSH x 9"},{"pid":"b89501e2f2ca25a5634b91a5f4d07904f92f74dc","tid":1468964,"uid":283657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T23:45:43.000Z","msg":"PUSH x 10"},{"pid":"cbee23a7ce35ffaef0aeead3475b6b7b50a87712","tid":1468964,"uid":283657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T23:47:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}